    <h3 style="padding-left: 12px;">About</h3>  
    <hr style="color:white;">
    <p style="font-size: 25px; padding: 10px;">
        This website tells you about the people of same interest ans lets you interact with them .
        You can also find the person with specific interest or with particular branch or year.
        This web-app's aim is to make it easier for others to find the person with specific details.
    </p>
    
<hr style="color:white;">
<h3 style="padding-left: 12px;">Features</h3>
<hr style="color:white;">

    <div class="row" style="padding: 25px;">
        <div class="col-4">
          <div class="list-group"  id="list-tab" role="tablist">
              <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active" id="profile-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#profile" role="tab" aria-controls="profile">Make profile</a>
              <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="update-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#update" role="tab" aria-controls="update">Update profile</a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="find-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#find" role="tab" aria-controls="find">Find </a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="explore-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#explore" role="tab" aria-controls="explore">Explore</a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="send-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#send" role="tab" aria-controls="send">Send mail</a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="view-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#view" role="tab" aria-controls="view">View profile</a>
            <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="login-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#login" role="tab" aria-controls="login">Login/Logout</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-8">
            <div class="tab-content" style="font-size: 25px; padding: 25px;" id="nav-tabContent">
                <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="profile" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="profile-list">Sign up with the specific details</div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="update" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="update-list">Update the specific field of your profile and keep it up to date</div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="find" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="find-list">Find the person with specific details by the help of find page of this website</div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="explore" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="explore-list">Explore other peoples profile with the help of home page</div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="send" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="send-list">Send mail to your friends by visiting their profile</div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="view" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="view-list">View your profile and see what other sees</div>
            <div class="tab-pane fade" id="login" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="login-list">Login/Logout anytime with the help of your private username and paasword and don't share it with anyone.</div>
        </div>
